title: DDFP 577: 'All or Nothing' and The Elimination Chamber with AJ Hawk
itunes:title: DDFP 577: 'All or Nothing' and The Elimination Chamber with AJ Hawk
description:
Dave Dameshek and actor Brian Baumgartner are joined by former NFL linebacker A.J. Hawk to kibitz about his new job at FS1, the second year of Amazon's "All or Nothing: A Season with the Los Angeles Rams" and the Hawk family tailgating rituals. Plus, Shek and the guys also played The Elimination Chamber: Decades of Music.
